---
layout: base.njk
title: Βίντεο
---
<main><section class="page-hero"><div class="wrap"><h1>Βίντεο</h1><p>Συνεντεύξεις, παρεμβάσεις και δημόσιες παρουσίες.</p></div></section><section class="section"><div class="wrap"><div class="grid video-grid">
{% set vids = collections.videos | reverse %}
{% for video in vids %}<a class="card reveal" href="{{ video.url }}">{% if video.data.thumbnail %}<div class="card-media"><img alt="{{ video.data.title }}" loading="lazy" src="{{ video.data.thumbnail }}"/></div>{% endif %}<span class="date">{{ video.data.displayDate | default(video.data.date) }}</span><h3>{{ video.data.title }}</h3></a>{% endfor %}
</div></div></section></main>